# Vietnamese Sentiment Analysis

## Overview

Vietnamese Sentiment Analysis is a Machine Learning project that classifies Vietnamese customer reviews into three sentiment categories:

* Negative (0)
* Neutral (1)
* Positive (2)

The project uses a traditional NLP pipeline including text preprocessing, TF-IDF feature extraction, and machine learning classifiers such as Logistic Regression and Linear SVM.

---

## Dataset

The dataset contains customer reviews with the following columns:

| Column  | Description          |
| ------- | -------------------- |
| content | Customer review text |
| label   | Sentiment label      |
| star    | Rating score         |

Label encoding:

```text
0 = Negative
1 = Neutral
2 = Positive
```

Dataset size:

* Total samples: ~31,000 reviews
* Classes: 3

